                                <date>1958</date>. С. <biblScope unit="page">??–??</biblScope>.</bibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><xi:include href="../encodingdesc.xml" parse="xml"/></teiHeader><text><body><entry xml:id="entry_kʼanʒol" xml:lang="os"><form type="lemma"><orth>kʼanʒol</orth></form><sense><abv:tr xml:lang="ru"><q>камзол</q></abv:tr><abv:tr xml:lang="en"><q>camisole</q></abv:tr></sense><etym xml:lang="ru">Из <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/> <w>камзол</w></mentioned>. Последнее — через <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/> <w>Kamisol</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fr"><lang/> <w>саmisole</w></mentioned> — к <mentioned xml:lang="it"><lang/> <w>camiciola</w> <gloss><q>фуфайка</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/> <gloss><q>майка</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/> <gloss><q>кофточка</q></gloss></mentioned> (уменьшительное к %icamicia%i ‘рубашка’). Сюда же <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/> <w>qoanzolg</w> <gloss><q>короткий бешмет</q></gloss></mentioned>.</etym><etym xml:lang="en">From <mentioned xml:lang="ru"><lang/> <w>камзол</w></mentioned>. The latter was borrowed through <mentioned xml:lang="de"><lang/> <w>Kamisol</w></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="fr"><lang/> <w>саmisole</w></mentioned> — to <mentioned xml:lang="it"><lang/> <w>camiciola</w> <gloss><q>jersey</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/> <gloss><q>undershirt</q></gloss></mentioned>, <mentioned xml:lang="it"><w/> <gloss><q>blouse</q></gloss></mentioned> (a diminutive form of %icamicia%i ‘shirt’). <mentioned xml:lang="inh"><lang/> <w>qoanzolg</w> <gloss><q>short beshmet</q></gloss></mentioned> is related to it as well.</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>